text: Achu-Yelga () is a rural locality (a village) in Kurdymsky Selsoviet, Tatyshlinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 69 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 35 km from Verkhniye Tatyshly, 10 km from Stary Kurdym. == References == Category:Rural localities in Tatyshlinsky District
title: Achu-Yelga
